  "meta": {
    "description": "Single-ingress router for all ERP → n8n events. Receives POST /webhook/erp-event-bus {event, emitted_at, payload}, routes on body.event to the appropriate sub-workflow. Unknown events fall through to Log unhandled event for observability."
  },
